{"color":"GREEN","isTrashed":false,"isPinned":false,"isArchived":false,"textContent":"Name: Potential Network\nObjective: Ikigai \nGame: build skills and acquire knowledge to accomplish Ikigai\nPlayer: humans with an avatar \nPlay: play, experiment and learn your way to your Ikigai by completing quests and leveling up. Apply these skills and knowledge to real world Ikigai practices.\n\n// Next step //\n\nMinimum viable product \nAn avatar\nA skill tree \nA system of evaluation \n\n// Deeper thoughts //\n\nOpen source game \nEvery role of life is a choice\nSkills are required \nSkill trees are created \nThe pathways are created \n\nYour character is the avatar\nYour unique ID capture the record of your life \nYour accomplishments become part of your skill tree\nEducational records \nHealth records \nPersonas\n\nJobs could see the holistic person\n\nThe person can see the jobs that are their ikigui\n\nPeople could see the path for their job \n\nEducation could become outcome based \n\nSpirituality could become integrated into life \n\n\nIs it a number? Is it a block chain? Is it a unique ID? Is it a social network profile?\n\nNever monetized \nAlways free \nAlways secure \n\nThe video games create the personas of the ikigui\n\nThe teacher, the warrior, the policeman, the marketer, the author \n\n\nThe skills are logged and croud sourced - and that algorithm is the core","title":"Potential Network","userEditedTimestampUsec":1702223545600000,"createdTimestampUsec":1702053915305000,"textContentHtml":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Name: Potential Network<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Go